intro_prompt:
Practice Info: In this practice session, you will need to identify one simple feeling and one simple need. Later practice sessions will require you to identify several feelings and needs.

Background: For this session imagine that you are having lunch with an old friend that you have not seen for a little while. You see your friend smiling when greet you her/him, but even from the first it seems like something is bothering your friend. They do not look like they are feeling particularly happy or healthy.
